This is a quick hack that can produce some awesome results:

<pre>
ExtFilterDefine imagecompress100 mode=output cmd="/usr/bin/convert - -resize 100 -"
ExtFilterDefine imagecompress200 mode=output cmd="/usr/bin/convert - -resize 200 -"
&lt;Location "/img/100/">
    SetOutputFilter imagecompress100
&lt;/Location>

&lt;Location "/img/200/">
    SetOutputFilter imagecompress200
&lt;/Location>
</pre>

Both /img/200/ and /img/200/ are just symlinks to /img/originals/.
